La Fortuna Drawing Library
By Ashley Lavery

To use this library you need to copy the lcd and drawing directories into your project.
Then include the drawing.h header file anywhere you want to use the library functions.
All the explanations functions for the library can be found in the header file.
You can find an example of how to use this library in the sample_main.c file.

This library supports drawing the outline and/or filling the following shapes.
- Pixel
- Line
- Rectangle
- Rounded Rectangle
- Circle
- Any polygon

The lcd library used is created by Steve Gunn and is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution License.
